---
// Hero section with beautiful gradient background and Avanish's personal touch
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Background with your image and purple gradients -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <!-- Main background image -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/firstPageBackground.jpeg');"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Purple gradient overlay at top -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-600/80 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Purple gradient overlay at bottom -->
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-purple-600/80 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Subtle pattern overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div
        class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full animate-bounce-gentle"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-40 right-32 w-1 h-1 bg-white rounded-full animate-bounce-gentle"
        style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-32 left-1/4 w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-white rounded-full animate-bounce-gentle"
        style="animation-delay: 1s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full animate-bounce-gentle"
        style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-1/2 left-10 w-1 h-1 bg-white rounded-full animate-bounce-gentle"
        style="animation-delay: 2s;"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
  >
    <div class="animate-fade-in">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-shadow-lg"
      >
        Avanish's Corner
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8 opacity-90"
      >
        Where words dance with emotions
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl opacity-80 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
      >
        नमस्ते! मैं अवनीश हूँ<br />
        यह स्थान मेरी कविताओं और विचारों के लिए है। हर लेखन मेरे मन का एक टुकड़ा
        है!
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg mt-4 opacity-70 px-2">
        Welcome to my little corner of the internet, where I share my thoughts,
        emotions, and experiences through the art of poetry. Each verse is a
        piece of my heart.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div
        class="mt-8 md:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-4 justify-center px-4"
      >
        <a
          href="/poems"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 rounded-full text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 touch-target"
        >
          Explore Poems
          <svg
            class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-white/50 rounded-full text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 touch-target"
        >
          About Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce"
  >
    <svg
      class="w-6 h-6 text-white/70"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    >
      <path
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        stroke-width="2"
        d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .text-shadow-lg {
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
</style>
